[INFO]    task-segment: [versions:display-plugin-updates]
[INFO] ------------------------------------------------------------------------
[INFO] [versions:display-plugin-updates]
[INFO]
[INFO] The following plugin updates are available:
[INFO]   maven-checkstyle-plugin .................................. 2.1 -> 2.2
[INFO]
